{
  "stem": "18626.11",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a bad name, bad word, not intelligent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, you are now in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And don't forget it for a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And don't think that Germany is going to lose the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because, you know, it was already done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was going-- the battle was going down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And don't forget, he says, that Deutschland is going kaput-- that Germany is going to be finished.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if [SPEAKING GERMAN], kaput, the whole world will go kaput.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The whole world will be finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And don't forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was sarcastic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he said, your President Rosenberg-- he didn't want to mention 'Roosevelt.' Your President Roosevelt-- Rosenberg knows it very well that we have a certain gift for him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he's going to get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because they were all talked into the atom bomb, which they were working on it all the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's going to be ready any day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And after the speech, he says, anybody who is not going to behave or who is going to do things against the rules of the camp, he's going to be shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And now, you're all a list.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you're going to go to give away all your private things, your private clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You're all prisoners of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And you're going to be numbered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And loose!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were all chased away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he walked away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then the other Germans took over the work, take away the clothes, you know, being watched, you know, observed, looked for things, pictures, everything you had to give away.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then they start to throw you the clothes, you know, the German prisoner clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Tall people grabbed, you know, clothes which is for short men.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
